    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8043-8d02-c026b876435a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Managing group works is often-times overwhelming for professors. The research presents a system that focuses on forming groups and allow usage of machine learning models to learning data to facilitate group formation.  A pilot-study on primary school is done and shows a positive effect of collaborative learning for disciplines such as math.",
